title: Bubba and Angela Get Real & Get Naughty

description:
Bubba and Angela, one of TikTok's cutest (and hottest) couples, join the show this week! They get freaky in a round of dirty Would You Rather with Bunnie, and Bubba comes clean about how a chicken nugget started their whole social media stardom. Angela shares how Bubba slid in her DM's, and what their first kiss was like. They also talk about jobs they held down before becoming TikTok famous, and what's next as they build their empire.
